edu.birzeit.swen6301.model

Class Segment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.birzeit.swen6301.model.Segment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPart, java.lang.Comparable, java.util.Comparator

    public class Segment
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPart, java.util.Comparator, java.lang.Comparable
    To encapsulate and organize all related specifications (links) of certain segment text.

    Main Functions:

    1. Split lines as text array of URLs.

    2. Bind URLs as mirror objects into attached list.

    3. Open stream of first available and valid mirror (URL).
